data.description: LAS VEGAS STRIP VIEWS! WEST MOUNTAIN VIEWS!  Property completely updated!  QUARTZ countertops throughout, new light fixtures/ceiling fans/baseboards. Kitchen features: NEW Kitchen Aid SS appliances, gas cooktop, designer tile backsplash and hood, Wet bar w SS sink/wine fridge, Great room feature wall w gas fireplace. All bathrooms have new Quartz countertops, new sinks, mirrors, shower surrounds, toilets, fixtures. Laundry room: new SAMSUNG washer/dryer, QUARTZ counter top, cabinets sink. Plantation shutters & blinds throughout, security film and solar screens for all windows. Water Softener, Water Heater, Water Filtration System, 2 HVAC systems all replaced in the last 2 years!  3 car insulated and cooled garage, storage, painted floors, Covered patio, built-in fireplace, fully fenced, travertine patio, planters, outdoor pet kennel with doggie door, raised viewing area to enjoy the Iconic LV Strip, Raiders practice facility, Executive Airport, and the Spectacular Spring Mountains...
